dct_title_s: Madgeburgum Ducatus cognominis metropolis ad albium, sub ditione regis Borussiæ : bene munitum ac florens emporium, in quo tribunal provinciale, consistorium et camer constituta
dct_description_sm: Map of Magdeburg in the German state of Saxony-Anhalt. Relief shown pictorially. Includes profile view of city below map. Tobias Conrad Lotter set up an independent publishing house in Augsburg in 1758. cf. Tooley's dict. of mapmakers.
dct_publisher_sm: Augsburg : Anjezo im Verlag beÿ Tobias Conrad Lotter, geogr., [between 1758 and 1777]
